{"tid":137744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警員截停違例司機捱撞","createTime":"2017-02-28T05:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T06:56:26.000Z","uid":5195,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56391abe9c4fa0beca32233b78bdb98ac112f0b1","tid":137744,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"上午11時18分，一名軍裝警員，在尖沙嘴金馬倫里驅趕違例泊車。一名男子駕駛私家車匆匆開車，但因為未扣安全帶被截停。惟司機疑手忙腳亂下再度開車，結果撞到警員的右腳小腿。警員通知控制室召救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n在附近工作的讀者黃先生指，「聽到出面有人抄牌，一名警員(向司機)呼喝，果個司機揸車調頭時撞到個差人。」黃先生稱，警員沒有跌倒，但小腿流血，立即召增援，10多名同僚趕到了解。黃聽到涉事司機向警方說：「咁你叫我調頭駛埋嚟，我咪駛埋嚟囉，點知你又唔避啫。」黃先生指警員就在私家車面前：「唔知佢係唔識揸車吖、度唔到個位吖，定係點，響佢面前都撞到，」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/131202_ad62ae0931634db5e5d4984ba7c28b95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F131202_ad62ae0931634db5e5d4984ba7c28b95.jpg&h=3cd99b0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce2aeb826835833ad6be17253a1ab6f4cb213c80","tid":137744,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:13:55.000Z","msg":"給我往死裡撞"},{"pid":"f436bd143d3c745355f3625b5093cb6f23fab774","tid":137744,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4662600a5ac0fa0274865f9ea0acde36533b63ee","tid":137744,"uid":13948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:16:18.000Z","msg":"個司機仆街喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecea29888e8660265597b68b8aea67f9c3703bb3","tid":137744,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"應該係扮蠢特登撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90e8ec2b50503ebdb91609ec618dcfa7a885249","tid":137744,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\